ps://api.github.com/users/kaworu","html_url":"https://github.com/kaworu","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kaworu/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kaworu/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kaworu/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kaworu/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kaworu/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kaworu/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kaworu/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kaworu/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kaworu/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-06-04t08:41:02z","updated_at":"2013-06-04t08:41:15z","body":"> a properly configured reverse proxy setup makes sure that owncloud gets the correct via remote_addr.\r\n\r\ncould you backup this claim with some documentation please ? i fail to see how a reverse proxy, by definition, can change a php variable. "},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/18901945","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/pull/1603#issuecomment-18901945","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/1603","id":18901945,"user":{"login":"bantu","id":189375,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/88483d87947219efecfc570465c753b2?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fcdc48f189c0e2e8a870f3d54615a2f0d.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"88483d87947219efecfc570465c753b2","url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu","html_url":"https://github.com/bantu","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-06-04t10:54:59z","updated_at":"2013-06-04t10:58:03z","body":"@kaworu i said \"reverse proxy setup\", not just \"reverse proxy\".\r\n\r\nthe proxy adds a header, e.g. \"x-real-ip\" containing the remote ip connecting to the proxy before forwarding the request to the webserver. the webserver checks whether the connecting remote ip is a valid proxy. if it is, it uses x-real-ip as the remote ip instead, which will be available to php.\r\n\r\nsee\r\nhttp://wiki.nginx.org/httpproxymodule\r\nhttp://wiki.nginx.org/httprealipmodule\r\nhttp://stderr.net/apache/rpaf/"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/18914434","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/pull/1603#issuecomment-18914434","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/1603","id":18914434,"user":{"login":"kaworu","id":109415,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/c14dadb0a6d5058d17b22c333998b9bc?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f5c90ea0e7bedb74b27852e5320d2e759.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"c14dadb0a6d5058d17b22c333998b9bc","url":"https://api.github.com/users/kaworu","html_url":"https://github.com/kaworu","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kaworu/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kaworu/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kaworu/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kaworu/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kaworu/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kaworu/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kaworu/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kaworu/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/k